data.description: GREAT PRICE REDUCTION! SELLER SAYS "GET THIS SOLD"  Low maintenance home at the end of a quiet street. No back yard neighbors but close to downtown Emmett. Many upgrades, custom cabinets, granite counters, barn door, tile back splash. Newer high efficiency HVAC & AC system (about 3 years old). Has a breakfast bar and 2 pantries.  Appliances are also about 3 years old. Master suite with marble walk in shower & walk-in closet. Covered patio for outdoor entertaining.  Beautiful views and no rear neighbors. All data is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer to verify all.
